<summary>
Specifically, where a defined policy blocks use of this feature, calls to <see cref="'Navigator.GetGamepads'."/> will throw a <c>SecurityError</c> <see cref="'DOMException'."/>. In addition, the <see cref="Window.Gamepadconnected_event."/> and <see cref="Window.Gamepaddisconnected_event."/> events will not fire.
</summary>
